text: And when the Lord shall have brought thee into the land of the Channonite, and the Hethite, and the Amorite, and the Hevite, and the Jebusite, which he swore to thy fathers, that he would give thee a land that floweth with milk and honey, thou shalt celebrate this manner of sacred rites in this month.
